MEN, I told you I had something for you!! 
Introducing my new clothing brand MERAKI “mer AH ki” this is something I have been working on for a while now and I was very hands on with creating this brand. From choosing a brand name, to actually making the logos myself and customizing the jogging suits on my own. Meraki is my newest business baby and starting out I have two Men’s Sets in blue and red that are dropping right now and currently AVAILABLE ONLINE now through my @glydestore website. I have men’s sizes medium- 3XL. Go to site in bio and scroll down to Meraki to place orders!!! If shipping is chosen it is 2-3 day USPS.
